Build Identifier: 4.0

in Yahoo mail when I click "reply" or "new mail" once in a while Omni.jar pops up in the command prompt. 

I'm scanning computer and always find one virus. (I was a victim of a spam sent from my yahoo account). So, I'm not sure if this is a bug or the "bug" (virus)

Reproducible: Sometimes

Steps to Reproduce:
1.in Yahoo mail click "reply"
2. in yahoo mail compose new mail
3.
Actual Results:  
clack screen of command prompt pops up with running lines

Expected Results:  
I can write the yahoo e-mail, prompt screen moves to the background

before it never happened, I made screen shots in JPG
